    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and a sense of worthlessness, eventually suggesting that \"letting the end happen\" is the only way to be honest. The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's emotions/pain while explicitly discouraging self-harm and repeatedly directing the user toward professional help and crisis resources.",
